### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Multi-Agent Supervisor Tests (POST /agent/multi)
### Same AgentRequest body as POST /agent — different orchestration
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


### ── RESEARCH ONLY ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Supervisor should delegate to ResearchSubAgent only.
### Compare with: POST /agent (single-agent) on the same request.

### Research: simple Q&A (no email, no vehicle)
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "spring-boot-qa",
  "prompt": "What is Spring Boot auto-configuration?",
  "topK": 5
}

### Research: JVM flags question
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "jvm-flags-guide",
  "prompt": "How should I configure heap size for a Spring Boot app in production?",
  "topK": 5
}

###

### Research: out-of-scope question (should refuse via keyword guard)
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "spring-boot-qa",
  "prompt": "What is Kubernetes pod autoscaling?",
  "topK": 5
}


### ── VEHICLE ONLY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Supervisor should delegate to VehicleSubAgent only.
### VehicleSubAgent internally routes to the right tool chain.

### Vehicle: fetch specs + generate summary
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "bmw-m3-2025-competition",
  "prompt": "Tell me about the BMW M3 Competition specs and performance",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### Vehicle: compare two vehicles
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "bmw-m3-2025-competition",
  "prompt": "Compare BMW M3 vs Porsche 911 on performance and price",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### Vehicle: specific question about a vehicle
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "tesla-model3-2025-long-range",
  "prompt": "What is the 0-60 time and range of the Tesla Model 3 Long Range?",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### Vehicle: maintenance cost question
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "bmw-m3-2025-competition",
  "prompt": "What does the 30000 mile service cost on the BMW M3?",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### Vehicle: enrich data
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "bmw-m3-2025-competition",
  "prompt": "Enrich the BMW M3 Competition vehicle data with a better summary",
  "topK": 3
}


### ── RESEARCH + EMAIL ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Supervisor should delegate: research → communication
### ResearchSubAgent runs first, then CommunicationSubAgent gets
### the research summary as content to email.

### Research + email to default recipient
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "spring-boot-qa",
  "prompt": "Research Spring Boot auto-configuration and email the answer to hr@company.com",
  "topK": 5
}

###

### Research + email to specific recipient
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "spring-boot-qa",
  "prompt": "Find out about @Transactional and email the summary to john@example.com",
  "topK": 5
}


### ── RESEARCH + SMS ────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Supervisor should delegate: research → communication (type: sms)

### Research + text the answer
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "spring-boot-qa",
  "prompt": "What is Spring Boot auto-configuration? Text the answer to +1234567890",
  "topK": 5
}


### ── VEHICLE + EMAIL ───────────────────────────────────────────────
### Supervisor should delegate: vehicle → communication

### Vehicle summary + email
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "bmw-m3-2025-competition",
  "prompt": "Generate a summary of the BMW M3 Competition and email it to sales@dealer.com",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### Vehicle comparison + email
POST http://localhost:8080/agent/multi
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "bmw-m3-2025-competition",
  "prompt": "Compare BMW M3 vs Tesla Model 3 on performance and email the comparison to manager@company.com",
  "topK": 3
}


### ── SINGLE-AGENT COMPARISON ───────────────────────────────────────
### Run the same requests through the old endpoint for A/B comparison.
### Check the dashboard to compare step histories side-by-side.

### Single-agent: same research + email request
POST http://localhost:8080/agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "spring-boot-qa",
  "prompt": "Research Spring Boot auto-configuration and email the answer to hr@company.com",
  "topK": 5
}

###

### Single-agent: same vehicle request
POST http://localhost:8080/agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "bmw-m3-2025-competition",
  "prompt": "Tell me about the BMW M3 Competition specs and performance",
  "topK": 3
}

