Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "top rated sports sedans",
  "topK": 5
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### DASHBOARD — check session histories after running the above
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List all sessions (both single-agent and multi-agent appear here)
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/dashboard

###

### Get a specific session's full state (replace {sessionId})
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/{sessionId}

###

### Get a specific session's step history (replace {sessionId})
GET http://localhost:8080/agent/{sessionId}/history
